## Summary of Changes

| Area | Change | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **Headers** | `helmet()` middleware | Removes `X-Powered-By`, adds `X-Content-Type-Options`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Referrer-Policy`, etc. |
| **Body size** | `limit: '10kb'` on parsers | Prevents payload-based DoS |
| **Rate limiting** | `express-rate-limit` | Protects against brute force & scraping |
| **Input validation** | Sanitize `page`/`limit` query params | Prevents NaN crashes and negative-index exploits |
| **Error handler** | 4-arg Express error middleware | Catches all thrown errors; never leaks stack traces |
| **404 handler** | Explicit 404 middleware | Prevents information leakage from default Express behaviour |
| **Process safety** | `unhandledRejection` / `uncaughtException` | Prevents silent failures and zombie processes |

